trans-unit.source: Represents an <xref uid="langword_csharp_<issuerNameRegistry>" name="<issuerNameRegistry>" href=""></xref> element in a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en <xref uid="langword_csharp_<issuerNameRegistry>" name="<issuerNameRegistry>" href=""> </xref> element i en konfigurasjonsfil.

trans-unit.source: The `<issuerNameRegistry>` element configures the issuer name registry.
trans-unit.target: Den `<issuerNameRegistry>` elementet konfigurerer utsteder navnet registeret.

trans-unit.source: The issuer name registry maps issuer tokens to a string name.
trans-unit.target: Utsteder navnet registeret tilordner utsteder-token til et navn på tilkoblingsstrengen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.IssuerNameRegistryElement.Type%2A> property (which represents the `type` attribute of the element) can be set to register a custom type.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.IssuerNameRegistryElement.Type%2A>egenskapen (som representerer den `type` -attributtet for elementet) kan angis for å registrere en egendefinert.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.IssuerNameRegistryElement.Type%2A>

trans-unit.source: By default, a type of <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.ConfigurationBasedIssuerNameRegistry> is assumed.

The `<issuerNameRegistry>` element can be specified at the service level under the `<identityConfiguration>` element or on a security token handler collection under the `<securityTokenHandlerConfiguration>` element.
trans-unit.target: Den `<issuerNameRegistry>` -element kan angis på tjenestenivå under den `<identityConfiguration>` element eller på en sikkerhet token behandlingsprogrammet samling under den `<securityTokenHandlerConfiguration>` elementet.

trans-unit.source: The `IssuerNameRegistry` property of the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.IdentityConfigurationElement> class and of the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.SecurityTokenHandlerConfigurationElement> class is an instance of IssuerNameRegistryElement.
trans-unit.target: Den `IssuerNameRegistry` -egenskapen for den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.IdentityConfigurationElement>klassen av den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.SecurityTokenHandlerConfigurationElement>klassen er en forekomst av IssuerNameRegistryElement.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.SecurityTokenHandlerConfigurationElement> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.IdentityConfigurationElement>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Configuration.IssuerNameRegistryElement"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Configuration.IssuerNameRegistryElement"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a string representation of the <xref:System.Type> of the issuer name registry.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en strengrepresentasjon av den <xref:System.Type>av utsteder navnet registeret.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: It corresponds to the `type` attribute of the `<issuerNameRegistry>` element.
trans-unit.target: Det samsvarer med den `type` for den `<issuerNameRegistry>` elementet.

trans-unit.source: If it is not specified, the property is `null`, a type of <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.ConfigurationBasedIssuerNameRegistry> is assumed.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den ikke er angitt i egenskapen er `null`, en type <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.ConfigurationBasedIssuerNameRegistry>antas.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.ConfigurationBasedIssuerNameRegistry>

trans-unit.source: The string representation of the <xref:System.Type> of the issuer name registry.
trans-unit.target: Strengrepresentasjon av den <xref:System.Type>av utsteder navnet registeret.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The type must derive from the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.IssuerNameRegistry"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Typen må være utledet fra den <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.IssuerNameRegistry"> </xref> klasse.
